data.description: Welcome Home! This gorgeous home is waiting for you to call it your own. Situated on a cult-de-sac, the home features a large two car garage, extra parking for RV or boat, 6ft privacy fence in backyard, storage shed and deck. The home has newer flooring, siding, roof and kitchen cabinets. The large fireplace in the living room and the gas fireplace downstairs are more than enough to heat this home, although you have electric for backup, the owners have never had to use it. Large 4 bed 2 bath with bathroom shower renovation, large laundry room and play room/workout area. This home has it all and is priced to move. Must see!
